text: Kim Woo-hong (; born 11 January 1995) is a South Korean footballer who plays as a winger for FC Seoul. == Club career == === FC Seoul=== Kim Woo-hong joined FC Seoul on 7 January 2018.Un ex madridista a punto de fichar por el FC Seoul He made his K League 1 debut on 1 September 2018 against Gangwon FC.'3연패' 서울, 강원과 대결서 '헛심 공방' 0-0 무승부 == References == == External links == * * Kim Woo-hong Profile Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:People from Yeongju Category:South Korean footballers Category:Association football wingers Category:UD Almería B players Category:Deportivo Fabril players Category:FC Seoul players Category:Segunda División B players Category:Tercera División players Category:K League 1 players Category:South Korea under-17 international footballers Category:South Korean expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Spain Category:South Korean expatriate sportspeople in Spain
